f=AI & Agents/DEPARTMENT-WORKFLOW.md · h1:Agents Department Workflow=**Built 2026-07-10 (all agents complete).** Owner: CAIO role. Law: `FLEET-CHARTER.md` (operator-owned; Engineering Security Charter senior). Plan: `AI-AGENTS-REDESIGN-PLAN.md` (approved, decisions resolved). · s=meta-department: builds (proto), connects (relay, scout), measures (gauge), diagnoses (forge), improves (anneal), gates (edge), governs (meta) agent fleet itself. signature design **closed improvement loop** catalog left dangling: detect diagnose fix verify. · h2:Working structure agents, pods=\| Pod \| Agents \| One-line job \| · h2:Working structure agents, pods=\|---\|---\|---\| · h2:Working structure agents, pods=\| Leadership \| **meta** ⭐ \| structural law, registries, charter custody, Rail 3 routing \| · h2:Working structure agents, pods=\| Lifecycle \| **proto**, **anneal** \| birth (caged experiments) and life (board-gated skill evolution) \| · h2:Working structure agents, pods=\| Methods \| **forge**, **edge** \| AI-method benchmarking/diagnosis and emerging-tech gating \| · h2:Working structure agents, pods=\| Integration \| **relay**, **scout** \| capability registry/grants/allowlist and ecosystem intake \| · h2:Working structure agents, pods=\| Observability \| **gauge** \| scorecards, golden runs, routing, the operator's health report \| · h2:Working tree improvement loop=`meta (law: standards \· registries \· charter custody) \· │ \· ├─ INTAKE:  scout scans ─► intake/skill-scouting ─► relay registers (least-privilege) \· │           edge gates tech ─► pilot specs ─► proto's cage ─► promote(Rail 3)/archive(learnings→anneal) \· │` · h2:Working instructions=**Nothing changes silently.** fleet change (skill edit, agent, model, threshold) written proposal board apply record re-measure (Fleet Charter Rail trivial-change tier operator decision 2026-07-10). **Nothing runs unregistered.** Tools/MCPs enter scout's intake relay's registry least-privilege grants egress allowlist quinn (Rails 1–2 authoring). **Nothing ships unbaselined.** Prototypes freeze criteria before building; skill edits cite demonstrated failure; benchmarks use shared golden set, blind replicated. **Everything ends purpose.** Prototypes get verdicts expiry (silence archive); flags end fixed/accepted/parked-with-a-date; watch entries carry triggers drop rules. **Boundaries (share, don't duplicate):** aegis owns LLM detection classes (referenced, never copied); quinn owns rails enforcement sandbox policy release gates; forge/gauge share ONE golden set (Rail 3-governed); model choice binds operator/platform config, never skills; kai owns business analytics; future Market Intelligence's radar owns market scanning. **Escalation:** charter ambiguity most-restrictive operator; security smells quinn+aegis immediately; stalled cases meta; board dormant proposals queue visibly, nothing auto-applies. · h2:Department pending (operator-side)=**Fleet Charter adoption**: fill `<FILL_IN>`s sign (until then: most-restrictive defaults)., **Golden task set** (shared forge/gauge) loudest gap; benchmarks provisional behavior-watching blind without it., **Governance docs** (constitution locked commitments) board dormant, anneal's edit path queues; anneal registered `dormant(board active)`., **Config `<FILL_IN>`s** across eight agents; **operator domain list** edge's landscapes; **forbidden-words list** anneal's audits., **Logical source books**: statistics/SPC (gauge+forge shared-statistics want vista/sentinel/nate/kai/rio), MCDA/decision analysis (edge+scout), maintenance economics (anneal), experimentation methodology (proto coordinate future Product dept), org-design measurement (meta), SRE/reliability (relay)., **Shared layer**: prompting-practices copy (anneal maintains content, queued), web-search capability (scout+edge heaviest consumers)., **Marketplace candidates queued scout's first pass**: hamelsmu/evals-skills (gauge), kodustech ETL-reliability (relay), llm-benchmarking sources (forge), writing-skills companion files (meta).